com.myronmarston.music
Class OutputManager

java.lang.Object
  com.myronmarston.music.OutputManager

public class OutputManager
extends java.lang.Object

Class that manages the outputs from FractalComposer, such as Midi files, WAV files, Mp3 files, PDF files of scores, etc.
